== Avocado Spread ==

Halve the @lime{1}.

Halve the @avocado{1} and remove the pit. Use a #tablespoon{} to scoop out the 
flesh into a #bowl{}. Mash with a #fork{}.

Season to taste with @salt{to taste}, @pepper{to taste} and a squeeze of lime 
juice.

Mix well and set aside.

== Bacon ==

Arrange the @Irish bacon{130%grams} on a lined #baking tray{}.

Bake on the top shelf of the oven until golden and crispy, ~{10-15%minutes}.

> IMPORTANT: Wash hands and equipment after handling raw meat. Cook bacon 
> thoroughly.

Place the @brioche buns{2} alongside to warm for the final ~{2%minutes}.

TIP: For an optional egg, place a pan over medium-high heat with a drizzle of 
oil. Crack in the egg (1 per person). Cook until the white is cooked and the 
yolk is your desired firmness, ~{4-5%minutes}.

== Sandwich Assembly ==

Spread @Ballymaloe Tomato Relish{1%pot} evenly over each bun base.

Top with the avocado, bacon and @grated cheese{50%grams}.

If you've made one, add your @?egg{2}.

Sandwich closed with the bun lid.